'''Marie-Clémence Andriamonta Paes''' (wavutse 1959), ni umukinnyi wa firime w’Abafaransa wo muri Malagasi .  Yakoze inyandiko nyinshi zamamaye cyane zirimo: ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' , ''Mahaleo'' na ''L'opéra du bout du monde'' . Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, ni producer numwanditsi. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1959 kuri se w’umufaransa na nyina wa Malagasy.  Yarangije impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri Sociology na Marketing CELSA-Sorbonne Diploma . 

Yashakanye na César Paes, akaba n'umuyobozi wa filimi uvuka muri Franco-Berezile. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1988, yatangije uruganda rwigenga rukorera i Paris rwitwa 'Laterit Productions' hamwe n'umugabo we César.  Isosiyete ikora ibicuruzwa yiyemeje gukwirakwiza no gutangaza. Hamwe numugabo we César Paes, yanditse kandi akora documentaire nka ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Umugani wo muri Madagasikari'' , ''Indirimbo n'amarira ya Kamere'', na ''Soup ya Awara'' . ''Awara Soup'' yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi muri Cinéma du Réel, Festival dei Popoli na Dok Leipzig . Filime ze nka ''Saudade do Futuro'', ''Mahaleo'', ''Opera yo mu nyanja y'Ubuhinde'' ''n'indirimbo za Madagasikari'' zasohotse mu ikinamico mu [[Bufaransa]] no muri [[Amerika]]. Muri documentaire ye, umuziki ni ikintu cyingenzi kandi umuziki ukoreshwa nkibintu byerekana inkuru. Amenshi muri firime ayobowe na Clémence yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi mu iserukiramuco rya Cinéma du Réel. 

